cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper describes the development of a robotic system that acquires knowledge incrementally through human interaction. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper describes a deep learning based localization and recognition system for object learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper describes the development of a system that acquires knowledge incrementally through human interaction and uses deep learning for object recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper describes the use of deep learning for object recognition. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper describes an intuitive user interface for specifying 3D motion tasks associated with new objects.
